What you need to know:  The hosts beat favourites Makerere University Business School (MUBS) 2-1 in the tough final attended by hundreds of KU’s studentsIn the third place play-off, defending champions University of Development Studies (UDS) from Ghana thrashed Makerere University 5-1The women’s crown went to University of Kinda who Thursday beat hosts KU 2-1 in their last match of the competition